    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，µpay是核心扣费队列。那参与的服务有哪些？我看到有AuthVault和FraudDetection，它们都是直接连到µpay吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
