    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AuthVault作为Service0连过来，时延是+0.1秒。FraudDetection作为User0连过去，时延是-0.1秒，表示它是前置校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service0",
        "User0",
        "dt = +0.1",
        "dt = -0.1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把µpay放到service smart contract子图里，加上Service0和User0的虚线连接，标注好时延。接下来µpay还要输出到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
