      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "µpay要分出两条线：一条到User1，也是TransactionQueue，作为下游队列；另一条到Service1，这是FraudDetection的另一个实例，做事后风控。",
      "elements_involved": [
